summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3018, for the improvement of Williams Court, from Fifteenth Avenue North to the west line of Williams Addition all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 36329 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
